record.title: ORDER FOR STAR PRINT--S. 589
record.narrative:
ORDER FOR STAR PRINT--S. 589 -- (Senate - November 13, 2007)

[Page: S14350]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. President, I ask unanimous consent that Calendar No. 474, S. 589, be star printed with the changes at the desk.

record.chair: Without objection, it is so ordered.

speaking.paragraph: Mr. President, I say to my friend, I am going to close the Senate. Does he want to say something?
